data.description: Welcome to this 2-story, 3 bedroom home located on a lovely fenced lot.  Step into the Living Room; notice the laminate floors that wrap through into the Kitchen/Eating, and Family Rm areas.  This home has a freshly painted neutral interior. Notice the open concept Family Rm / Kitchen.  The Kitchens eating area has a sliding glass door that leads onto the patio. Take a look at this nice sized backyard. Updates include a new roof, and Garden window in the Kitchen.  Located near park, shopping and dining. Schedule your tour!
